<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Recovery Management Inc.
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body background=stone.jpg>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="images/rmi_l.gif">
<IMG SRC="images/rmi4.gif">
</CENTER>
<P>
Welcome to the Recovery Management, Inc. (RMI) home page.  RMI
produces software productivity tools designed to assist with the
development, implementation and maintenance of a Business Recovery
Plan.  These productivity tools known as REXSYS for DOS, REXSYS
for Windows and REX/Collect are supported by RMI with Consulting,
Training and Telephone Assistance.<HR>

