<HEAD>

</HEAD>
<body background=stone.jpg>
<BODY LINK ="#07A6F4" VLINK="#0766F4" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<IMG SRC="images/rmirex.gif">
<P>
REXSYS provides all of the basics that a high caliber contingency
planning software package demands; however, the power of REXSYS
rest with its most salient and unique features.  REXSYS offers
the competitive advantage of a fully functional Business Impact
Analysis component which places expert system technology at the
user's fingertips, eliminating subjective determination and enabling
the sound rating of time critical business functions and applications.
 The task of managing constantly changing data base information
along with comprehensive procedures and narrative is accomplished
by the seamless integration of a relational data base and state-of-the-art
word processing technology.  With REXSYS, the terms user friendly,
flexibility, graphical user interface, on-line hyper-text help,
automated data collection and on-site training are all simply
redefined as benefits.  For the organization in need of business
recovery planning software, REXSYS is the solution.
