<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Recovery Management, Inc.
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY LINK ="#07A6F4" VLINK="#0766F4" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"> 

<P>
<B>REX/Collect</B>
<P>
REX/Collect, the data gathering utility for your PC-based REXSYS
business recovery planning system, makes it easy to collect information
from any department or functional area..... no matter where its
located.  The concept of REX/Collect is that the Plan Coordinator
will distribute electronic forms to each functional area and receive
the procedures and resource requirements from each functional
area for inclusion in the contingency plan.
<P>
REXSYS can run on a LAN, WAN or stand alone.  It will produce
paper data collection forms or can collect data live.  REX/Collect
provides the REXSYS user an electronic alternative to collect
vital information at the functional/departmental level.
<P>
With REX/Collect you'll:
<UL>
<LI>Save time
<LI>Save money
<LI>Eliminate paperwork
<LI>Improve data accuracy
<LI>Speed plan development
<LI>Create a better plan
</UL>

<P>

<P>
Information on REX/Collect is sent with REXSYS literature
<P>
<A HREF="order.html">Go to REXSYS info.</A>
<P>
<A HREF="index.html">Return to RMI main screen</A>
