<P>
<B>RMI Consulting Services</B>
<P>
Recovery Management, Inc. can help you develop a custom business
recovery plan that takes into account the unique way you do business.
 RMI offers a complete range of services and products that make
recovery planning easier than you ever imagined.
<P>
Services:
<IMG SRC="images/rmi2.gif"ALIGN=RIGHT>
<UL>
<LI>Executive Seminars
