<LI>Needs Assessment
<LI>Business Impact Analysis (BIA)
<LI>Information Gathering/Verification
<LI>Plan Development
<LI>Plan Implementation
<LI>Plan Testing
<LI>Plan Maintenance
</UL>

<P>

<P>
Using a RMI consultants to assist you in the business recovery
planning process is like having skilled navigators at your side.
 RMI consultants are experts in every aspect of business recovery
planning.  Our consultants carry the Certified Disaster Recovery
Planners (CDRP) designation.
<P>
There's no charge for an initial discussion of your situation,
either in person or over the phone.  Perhaps you only need our
REXSYS planning system.  Or, maybe your needs are more involved
and/or you simply don't have the time to develop a plan on your
own - we can help you do it fast, efficiently and as cost-effectively
as possible.  Call us today!
