</BODY><center>
<font size=6>When A Ruptured<br> Water Main<br> Pounded Penton<br> Publishing,<br> REXSYS<br> Helped Speed<br> Recovery</font size></center>
<br>
<img src="images/rmi7.gif" image align=left>
<br><br><font size=6><right><Em>"Our REXSYS business recovery plan worked to perfection!"</font size></em><br><font size=4>Susan Grimm, VIce President<br>
Penton Publishing, Inc.<br><br><br><br>
<font size=7>O</font size>n a frigid morning last winter, a broken water main showered the first four floors of Penton Publishing's Cleveland headquarters with a million gallons of water and large chunks of Superior Ave.  Fifteen of the company's 35 magazines were directly affected.<br>
<br>Guided by REXSYS, the business recovery planning system from Recovery Management, Inc., and working round-the-clock, the Penton recovery teams "got down to work and did exactly what they were supposed to do," says Penton vice president, Susan Grimm.<br>
<br>Within hours, Penton was up and running and within two weeks was at full strength.  "We used REXSYS to build a database of recovery plans, including the names and phone numbers of employees on recovery teams.  The REXSYS design made it easy to update the system with what we learned from this disaster.  The fact that we discussed and planned for disaster recovery gave us the confidence and knowledge to recover quickly," Grimm explained.<br>
<br>Windows-based REXSYS is easy to use and provides all the tools you'll need to quickly create a plan to protect your business.  Call Recovery Management, Inc. today at 1-800-764-8866<br>
<br><font size=6>
Boston<br></font size>
435 King Street<br>
Littleton, Mass.  01460<br>
800-RMI-8866<br>
FAX (508) 486-0060<br>
