<dd>	The group rate is $97 for a single room and $107 for a double room. To reserve a room, please contact the Hyatt Regency	directly at (404) 577-1234 ext. 4810. The conference hotel will hold a limited number of rooms until 30 days prior to the conference dates.  Be sure to make your reservations as early as possible.  Mention that you are a Disaster Recovery Conference attendee to receive the special conference rate for your hotel room.<br><br>
