<dd>	The fee must be paid prior to this event.   Please send your payment with your registration, or we will bill your company 	if you desire.<br><br>
Seminar Hours:  <br>
<dd>	Registration will be available from 5:30 - 8:00 p.m. on Sunday, September 8 and from 7:15-8:15 a.m. on Monday, September 		9. The seminar hours will be from 8:15 a.m. to 5:30 p.m. on Monday, September 9, 8:15 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. on Tuesday, 			September 10, and from 8:15 a.m. to 1 p.m. on Wednesday, September 11. <br><br>
Conference Fee: <br>
<dd>	Conference fee is $895.00 per person.  Early registration discounts are available as follows:  <br>	
<dd>	Before July 10, 1996-------------------$695.00 per person<br>
<dd>	July 11 through August 7-------------$795.00  per person<br>
<dd>	August 8 through Sept. 9--------------$895.00 per person<br><br>
<dd>
<dd>	Fee includes all conference materials, notebook, continental breakfasts, luncheons and participation in the workshop 			forums and breakout sessions. Fee also includes a welcome reception on Sunday evening and a hospitality on Monday evening. 		Hotel accommodations, airfare, car rental, CDRP exam and DRI courses are not included.  	<br>	<br>

DRI International CDRP Examination Fee:<br>
<dd>	The CDRP Examination fee is $200.00.  This includes fees for processing the Application for Certification through the DRI International, 1810 Craig Rd. Suite 125, St. Louis, MO  63146, (314) 434-2272.<br><br>

DRI International Course Fees:<br>
<dd>	The DRI International course fee for seminar participants is $499.00.  This fee includes the CDRP Examination for those  taking any of the courses. The fee for non-seminar attendees is $595.00 per course.<br><br>
Airfare Discounts:<br>
<dd>	Group rates for airfare will be offered. Detailed information will be provided with registration. Certain restrictions will apply.<br><br>
Cancellation Policy (MUST BE IN WRITING):<br>
<dd>	Cancellations made 30 days prior to the first day of the seminar will be refunded in full.  Cancellations after that 	date are subject to a 23% service charge.  All "no shows" will be charged the full amount. 


