<TITLE>Exhibitor Contract </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body background="stone.jpg">
<BODY>
<b>
<center><blink>Please Print this Form out and Fax to (314) 894-7474.</blink><b><br><br><br>
Eighth International Disaster Recovery Symposium and Exhibition<br>
                 September 9-11, 1996 Atlanta, GA<br>
             APPLICATION AND EXHIBIT SPACE CONTRACT</center><br>
<br>
This application for exhibit space at the Eighth International Disaster Recovery Symposium and Exhibition, which will become a contract with the Disaster
Recovery Journal (herein called ‘SPONSOR") upon written acceptance, is based upon the terms set forth below and on the reverse side hereof and the
plan of exhibits, rates, and the rules end regulations as may be established from time to time set forth in this contract as updated and amended, end general
exhibit information attached to this form, all of which constitute a part of this contract.<br>
<br>
     1. EXHIBIT SPACE RENTAL FEE: THE RENTAL FEE FOR EXHIBIT SPACE IS ONE THOUSAND ONE HUNDRED AND NINETY FIVE
DOLLARS ($1195) FOR A 8 FOOT BY 10 FOOT BOOTH. THE RENTAL FEE FOR A CORNER EXHIBIT SPACE IS ONE THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED
NINETY FIVE DOLLARS ($1295). IF YOU ARE REGISTERING FOR BOTH THE MARCH AND ME SEPTEMBER SEMINARS THE RENTAL FEE IS NINE
HUNDRED AND NINTY FIVE DOLLARS (5995) FOR EACH SHOW. THE RENTAL FEE FOR A CORNER BOOTH AT EACH SHOW IS ONE THOUSAND
NINETY FIVE DOLLARS ($1095). THE FEE INCLUDES STANDARD DRAPERY EQUIPMENT AND A 7 INCH X 44 INCH SIGN. EXHIBITOR MUST
NOTIFY SPONSOR AS TO THE NAME ON THE SIGN.<br>
<br>
O Check here if registering for consecutive conferences.<br>
<br>
     2. PAYMENT TERMS: The full amount is due upon receipt of invoice. When the payment is received. SPONSOR will mail EXHIBITOR booth
location forms.<br>
<br>
     3. ASSIGNMENT OF EXHIBIT LOCATION: SPONSOR will make every effort to comply with requests for assignment of exhibit space locations
on a "first-come/first-served" basis for those EXHIBITORS that have returned the contract and payment in full.<br>
<br>
     4. SIZE OF EXHIBIT SPACE REQUESTED: Size  __________ ft., x   __________ ft.<br>
     5. Do not wish to be near___________________________________________________<br>
     Wish to be near___________________________________________________________<br>
<br>
     6. STATEMENT OF THE NATURE OF THE EXHIBITORS’ BUSINESS AND TYPE OF PRODUCTS TO BE DISPLAYED (use separate sheet
if necessary): This item must be completed and the exhibit will be limited to the display described below. Any changes in the exhibit are subject to the written
approval of the SPONSOR. Please note that the use of exhibit space is subject to the restrictions described on the reverse side hereof. EXHIBITOR
authorizes the SPONSOR to publish the following information in the Program brochures.<br>
<br>
Exhibitors Business:____________________________________________________________________________________________<br><br>
