<center><p align=center>

This is the experimental home page of <i>The Economist</i>. It is the on-line home for a limited selection of articles from the current issue; The Economist Review, a monthly books and multimedia supplement to <i>The Economist</i>; and several of our surveys. We plan to add more to the site as well as offer more information and products from The Economist Group. <p>


Our business editor, John Micklethwait, and our management editor, Adrian Wooldridge, have just published a critical guide to the management gurus and their effect on government, business and society around the world, <a href="http://airwolf.ivision.co.uk">The Witch Doctors</a>.
<p>

Receive Politics This Week and Business This Week summaries by e-mail.<br>You can arrange your <a href="http://www.economist.com/mailing/">free subscription</a> from this site.

