<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Economist</TITLE></HEAD><img src="econlogosmall.gif" alt="The Economist Logo"></td><td align=center valign=top></HEAD><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><BODY><ul><H1>The weekly journal of ideas and analysis</H1><P><I>The Economist</I> is a weekly news and opinion newspaper offeringreporting, commentary and analysis on world politics, global business,finance and economics, science and technology and the arts.<P>Founded in 1843 to support the cause of free trade, the newspaperhas remained true to its mission ever since. Today, <I>The Economist</I>is firmly established as one of the world's most influential andauthoritative publications.<P><I>The Economist</I> differs from all other major news and opinionpublications in having a unique separation of ownership from the  editorial staff; it also differs in the anonymity of its contribution. These guarantee <i> The Economist</i> a truly independent single voice.<P>With a circulation in excess of 600,000, <I>The Economist</I>is read by opinion-formers in more than 180 countries around theworld.<HR></ul><P><br><p align=center><a href="index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a></BODY></HTML>
