<html><head><title>The Economist</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<p align=center><img src="http://www.economist.com/homeheader.gif" width="430" height="28" alt="" border=0></p>
<p align=center><a href="econ.html"><img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogolarge.gif" width="190" height="95" alt="The Economist" border=0></a></p>




<center><p align=center>

This is the experimental home page of <i>The Economist</i>. It is the on-line home for a limited selection of articles from the current issue; The Economist Review, a monthly books and multimedia supplement to <i>The Economist</i>; and several of our surveys. We plan to add more to the site as well as offer more information and products from The Economist Group. <p>


