http://www.economist.com:80/surveys/techfn/tf1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113131736 text/html 6677
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:13:48 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 25-Oct-96 10:25:34 GMT
