http://www.economist.com:80/surveys/banking/ibsu1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113132631 text/html 15397
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:22:44 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:04:13 GMT
