http://www.economist.com:80/issue/14-12-96/sf0803.html 199.173.162.110 19970113134840 text/html 22410
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:44:54 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 12-Dec-96 17:07:49 GMT
