<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/07-12-96/ld4467.html 199.173.162.110 19970113135322 text/html 9175
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:49:31 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 05-Dec-96 18:58:43 GMT
