http://www.economist.com:80/issue/07-12-96/sf0797.html 199.173.162.110 19970113135457 text/html 21379
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:51:12 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 05-Dec-96 19:08:49 GMT
