<DOCNO>WT21-B37-251</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000272-B033-166</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/07-12-96/br7629.html 199.173.162.110 19970113135754 text/html 6142
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:54:04 GMT
