<DOCNO>WT21-B37-258</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000272-B033-391</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/07-12-96/mo0311.html 199.173.162.110 19970113140101 text/html 20827
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 13:57:12 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 05-Dec-96 18:46:36 GMT
Content-length: 20641
